  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nThe biggest pain point of the debugger is stepping through the functions to arrive at the exact code location that you are interested in. Being able to start the debugger at the exact code location could be really helpful. To make things easier on building this feature, this could only be activated/in-use if `forge test --debug` is being called.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
